{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the name of the school, because in our place, they had a Catholic school and they had a Protestant school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Same thing, they had the church, the Protestant Church and the Catholic church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, as a little girl, during the war I had to go up to the steeple of the Protestant church.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they gave me a binocular that we should watch if the airplanes are coming, not that it would do any good.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have the telephone up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have any way, except we would holler that the plane is coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The plane is coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, sometimes I was thinking of it that there was a movie, that the plane is coming, the plane.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they sent me up there to see if the plane is coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And to go back to the holidays, we had Rosh Hashanah, which was a beautiful holiday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The whole family went to shul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Yom Kippur, the whole family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When you were at least the age of 10, you were supposed to fast all day long, if not a half a day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were people who would faint in the shul from the fasting, so they would use this Quincy apple, put under the nose or something like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then we had-- as I mentioned before, we had Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had Purim.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My brother would dress up in a woman clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he really looked very funny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were laughing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had lot of funs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he would go from house to house and he would say the Purim spiel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he would come home with some coins that he had gotten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Our-- our mother would send the [NON-ENGLISH] to another friend of hers with all the goodies.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
